Prepare Bootstrap (requires internet):

1. install python3 (for http web server)
2. install ansible
3. download images:
  a. CoreOS.iso
  b. portainer.tar.bz2
  c. traefik.tar.bz2
  d. nexus.tar.bz2
4. download volume backups from onedrive

Bootstrap install:

(Portainer):
1. start python http server
2. connect to coreOS over SSH
  a. download, load, and start portainer-image from bootstrap-http
  b. add dns entry for portainer-backend01
  c. ensure container traefik tags exist

Bootstrap install:

(Traefik):
1. start python http server
2. connect to coreOS over SSH
  a. download, load, and start traefik-image from bootstrap-http
  b. if backup secret exists:
    TRUE: configure traefik to use cloudflare and creds (ansible-secret-vault)
    FALSE: generate fresh config to generate secret
  c. add dns entries for traefik

  b. download, load, and start nexus-image from bootstrap-http
